      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Mathieu Pagé</b>\n</p><p><b>Mathieu Pagé</b>,<br />\na Canadian software devloper in the insurance induytry and as avocational computer chess programmer author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/MatMoi\" title=\"MatMoi\">MatMoi</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, \nunder development approximately since 2003. MatMoi 7.15.0, which played the <a href=\"/CCT12\" title=\"CCT12\">CCT12</a>, was published as free engine in March 2010 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mathieu_Pag%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mathieu_Pag%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=312031\">The need to unmake move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Unmake_Move\" title=\"Unmake Move\">Unmake Move</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mathieu_Pag%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=425470\">Re: Chess program crash generator (MatMoi did not crash)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=436702\">Opponent-modeling in computer chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 14, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Opponent_Model_Search\" title=\"Opponent Model Search\">Opponent Model Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=477208\">Is there an overhead in this OO design&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=19779\">Repetition detection structure</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=19867\">Transposition Table and nps drop</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nodes_per_second&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nodes per second (page does not exist)\">Nodes per second</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=22274\">Is 64 bits enough as a hash length</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 10, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23257\">When and how to return a draw evaluation?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 26, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Draw\" title=\"Draw\">Draw</a>, <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23727\">Effect of MVV/LVA</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, Sepember 14, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV-LVA</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=24198\">Nodes type clarification</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 05, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Node_Types\" title=\"Node Types\">Node Types</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=24357\">How is SEE used?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  October 13, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=25705\">Draw by repetition when mate is possible</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a>, <a href=\"/Checkmate\" title=\"Checkmate\">Checkmate</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26130\">Running very fast games in xboard</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 20, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/XBoard\" title=\"XBoard\">XBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28438\">Time managment on ponder hit</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 16, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">Time Management</a>, <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31129\">xboard and wine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 18, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mathieu_Pag%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31479\">Question about SEE algorithm on Chessprogramming Wiki</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/SEE_-_The_Swap_Algorithm\" title=\"SEE - The Swap Algorithm\">SEE - The Swap Algorithm</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=33035\">Efficiently index material signatures and lookup</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 03, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a>, <a href=\"/Material_Tables\" title=\"Material Tables\">Material Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=33222\">When do you probe the EGTB</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 12, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=33279\">MatMoi 7.15.0-cct, a Windows/Linux chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 15, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39957\">PGN Parser Interface in C</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 05, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45571\">Chess game data structure in C</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46075\">SAN parser within a PGN parser</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48116\">Check move validity for a pinned pieces</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 26, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48322\">Extract direction (ray) informations from two squares</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Rays\" title=\"Rays\">Rays</a>, <a href=\"/Square_Attacked_By\" title=\"Square Attacked By\">Square Attacked By</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mathieu_Pag%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55170\">A new chess engine&#160;: m8 (comming not so soon)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 01, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66588\">Learning piece-square table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mathieu Pagé</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mathieu_Pag%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mathieupage.com/\">Mathieu Pagé - Blog</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mathieupage.com/index.php/matmoi-chess-engine/\">MatMoi (Chess engine) | Mathieu Pagé</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mathieupage.com/index.php/2013/05/04/fen-database/\">FEN Database | Mathieu Pagé</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mathieupage.com/index.php/photographie/\">Photographie – Mathieu Pagé</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mathmoi\">Mathieu Pagé | Facebook</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/mathieupage\">Mathieu Pagé | Flickr</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mathieu_Pag%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\